body: This is the result of a [recent change](https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Butterfly/commit/7c403ad2f50eaf4ec2e10bcbdaa6aa68ee7f3a6a). You need to [update butterfly](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/xn/detail/2985220:Comment:1585631), and try again. You need to restart Rhino and Grasshopper. In case you don't want to run the analysis again, once you update butterfly you can use the new component to load the probes using the project name. [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/DmYnIaXFmPpoGUS-i32DvQnskvRjdbdvFMBmU6tyVHU7XgARNVAAYL6N78e7orkxXWJMKFOkI3pf9uqU4*1mNXOdaj1kH3o0/butterfly_loadProbesFromProject.jpg)
